#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.43"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.43:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.43:0.2"
msgid "5. Jarāvagga"
msgstr "5. Old Age"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.43:0.3"
msgid "43. Sāketasutta"
msgstr "43. At Sāketa"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.43:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "sn48.43:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sākete viharati añjanavane migadāye."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāketa in the deer part at the "
"Añjana Wood."

msgctxt "sn48.43:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn48.43:1.4"
msgid ""
"“atthi nu kho, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma yāni pañcindriyāni "
"tāni pañca balāni honti, yāni pañca balāni tāni pañcindriyāni hontī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, is there a way in which the five faculties become the five "
"powers, and the five powers become the five faculties?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.43:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā bhagavaṃnettikā bhagavaṃpaṭisaraṇā. Sādhu "
"vata, bhante, bhagavantaṃyeva paṭibhātu etassa bhāsitassa attho. Bhagavato "
"sutvā bhikkhū dhāressantī”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. He is our guide and our refuge. "
"Sir, may the Buddha himself please clarify the meaning of this. The "
"mendicants will listen and remember it.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.43:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Atthi, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma yāni pañcindriyāni tāni "
"pañca balāni honti, yāni pañca balāni tāni pañcindriyāni honti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there is a way in which the five faculties become the five "
"powers, and the five powers become the five faculties."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.43:4.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma yāni pañcindriyāni tāni "
"pañca balāni honti, yāni pañca balāni tāni pañcindriyāni honti?"
msgstr "And what is that method?"

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, saddhindriyaṃ taṃ saddhābalaṃ, yaṃ saddhābalaṃ taṃ "
"saddhindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of faith is the power of faith, and the power of faith is the "
"faculty of faith."

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.3"
msgid "yaṃ vīriyindriyaṃ taṃ vīriyabalaṃ, yaṃ vīriyabalaṃ taṃ vīriyindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of energy is the power of energy, and the power of energy is the "
"faculty of energy."

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.4"
msgid "yaṃ satindriyaṃ taṃ satibalaṃ, yaṃ satibalaṃ taṃ satindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of mindfulness is the power of mindfulness, and the power of "
"mindfulness is the faculty of mindfulness."

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.5"
msgid ""
"yaṃ samādhindriyaṃ taṃ samādhibalaṃ, yaṃ samādhibalaṃ taṃ samādhindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of immersion is the power of immersion, and the power of "
"immersion is the faculty of immersion."

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.6"
msgid "yaṃ paññindriyaṃ taṃ paññābalaṃ, yaṃ paññābalaṃ taṃ paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The faculty of wisdom is the power of wisdom, and the power of wisdom is the "
"faculty of wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.7"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, nadī pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā pācīnapabbhārā, tassa "
"majjhe dīpo."
msgstr ""
"Suppose that there was a river slanting, sloping, and inclining to the east, "
"and in the middle was an island."

#. VAR: saṅkhyaṃ → saṅkhaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn48.43:4.8"
msgid ""
"Atthi, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma tassā nadiyā eko sototveva "
"saṅkhyaṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"There’s a way in which that river can be reckoned to have just one stream."

msgctxt "sn48.43:4.9"
msgid ""
"Atthi pana, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma tassā nadiyā dve "
"sotānitveva saṅkhyaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr ""
"But there’s also a way in which that river can be reckoned to have two "
"streams."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.220"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.43:5.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma tassā nadiyā eko "
"sototveva saṅkhyaṃ gacchati?"
msgstr ""
"And what’s the way in which that river can be reckoned to have just one "
"stream?"

#. VAR: purimante → puratthimante (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn48.43:5.2"
msgid ""
"Yañca, bhikkhave, tassa dīpassa purimante udakaṃ, yañca pacchimante udakaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"By taking into account the water to the east and the west of the island,"

msgctxt "sn48.43:5.3"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma tassā nadiyā eko "
"sototveva saṅkhyaṃ gacchati."
msgstr "that river can be reckoned to have just one stream."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.43:6.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma tassā nadiyā dve "
"sotānitveva saṅkhyaṃ gacchanti?"
msgstr ""
"And what’s the way in which that river can be reckoned to have two streams?"

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.2"
msgid ""
"Yañca, bhikkhave, tassa dīpassa uttarante udakaṃ, yañca dakkhiṇante udakaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"By taking into account the water to the north and the south of the island,"

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.3"
msgid ""
"ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pariyāyo yaṃ pariyāyaṃ āgamma tassā nadiyā dve "
"sotānitveva saṅkhyaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr "that river can be reckoned to have two streams."

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.4"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, yaṃ saddhindriyaṃ taṃ saddhābalaṃ, yaṃ saddhābalaṃ "
"taṃ saddhindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, the faculty of faith is the power of faith, and the power "
"of faith is the faculty of faith."

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.5"
msgid "yaṃ vīriyindriyaṃ taṃ vīriyabalaṃ, yaṃ vīriyabalaṃ taṃ vīriyindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of energy is the power of energy, and the power of energy is the "
"faculty of energy."

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.6"
msgid "yaṃ satindriyaṃ taṃ satibalaṃ, yaṃ satibalaṃ taṃ satindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of mindfulness is the power of mindfulness, and the power of "
"mindfulness is the faculty of mindfulness."

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.7"
msgid ""
"yaṃ samādhindriyaṃ taṃ samādhibalaṃ, yaṃ samādhibalaṃ taṃ samādhindriyaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"The faculty of immersion is the power of immersion, and the power of "
"immersion is the faculty of immersion."

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.8"
msgid "yaṃ paññindriyaṃ taṃ paññābalaṃ, yaṃ paññābalaṃ taṃ paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The faculty of wisdom is the power of wisdom, and the power of wisdom is the "
"faculty of wisdom."

msgctxt "sn48.43:6.9"
msgid ""
"Pañcannaṃ, bhikkhave, indriyānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā bhikkhu āsavānaṃ "
"khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā "
"sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"It’s because of developing and cultivating the five faculties that a "
"mendicant realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in "
"this very life. And they live having realized it with their own insight due "
"to the ending of defilements.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.43:6.10"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
